metadata.name: Istanbulite
metadata.description:
City which connects continents, cultures and many many more... Istanbul. 

Composite.

One shot of skyline of European Side of Istanbul at night. 
One shot of Bosphorus Bridge of Istanbul at night.
One Shot of Marmara Sea under flash light at night. 

Composited to reflect the aura of 'never sleeping city', Istanbul. 

1/1 Edition.
